{"tid":1513410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警世」筲箕灣出現大陸呃食黨 專呃老人家錢","createTime":"2019-08-28T10:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:00:38.000Z","uid":95274,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8a63162e3668bf000b74cf524d4a02716539a519","tid":1513410,"uid":95274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:14:43.000Z","msg":"大約一個月前遇上兩個大陸女人，問我可唔可以比廿蚊比佢地買野食，事關我趕時間，馬上拒絕頭也不回。<br />\n今日收工又見到佢地出街搵食，見到個呀伯都幾醒拒絕左，我就趁機影佢地相，比大家警世。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rFRVCEP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrFRVCEP.png&h=caaf5f81&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CCCNtMA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCCCNtMA.png&h=e337c7a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wowOddm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwowOddm.png&h=090deeb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然佢地發現左我影佢地相<br />\n佢地行蹤敗露 就用「走住屌」既技能<br />\n一路講SB一路急腳走<br />\n我就笑住拎住手機對住佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1766b852f9bff00049c92a035058af825eb2f266","tid":1513410,"uid":12447,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少有高質相<br />\n無手震、對蕉準確"},{"pid":"33160c9611d151cfeee119add7eba563dfe35d6b","tid":1513410,"uid":38175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:22:18.000Z","msg":"推 一時好心無好結果"},{"pid":"66ba0f7fcd7c2bfd63b75cd637cad3d0e203af65","tid":1513410,"uid":119688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"一睇就知大陸雞樣"},{"pid":"64224e91442b7eefc0f8b4950f7c8baf0f4ca660","tid":1513410,"uid":146245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06df27491d708f961b5a22104efe76bf2cb983c1","tid":1513410,"uid